(25918, 'Respenzo 600 mg 10 f.c.tabs.', 'ريسبنزو 600مجم 10 اقراص', '144', '206', 'Linezolid', 'Sigma > hochster pharmaceutical industries', 'Tab', 'أقراص', 'مضاد حيوي', 'Antibiotic.oxazolidinone', '600 mg', 'Linezolid is indicated in adults and children for the treatment of infections caused by susceptible Gram-positive bacteria, including nosocomial pneumonia, community-acquired pneumonia, skin and skin structure infections, and vancomycin-resistant _Enterococcus faecium_ infections.[L32965] Examples of susceptible bacteria include _Staphylococcus aureus_, _Streptococcus pneumoniae_, _Streptococcus pyogenes_, and _Streptococcus agalactiae_.[L32965]
